  <brief_title>Creating Smokefree Living Together for Chinese Household Pairs</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;Creating Smokefree Living Together&quot;: Smokefree Counseling Intervention for Chinese Smokers and Household Nonsmokers</official_title>
